{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"zettel.20260420060847","title":"Arsitektur adalah penentu biaya perubahan masa depan","desc":"Fowler: istilah architecture kabur, tetapi yang penting adalah bahwa arsitektur menentukan betapa lambat dan mahalnya perubahan berikutnya.","tags":["permanent-note","software-architecture","architecture","cost-of-change"],"custom":{},"fname":"zettel.20260420060847","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"de5e919c62c79f451d4c2405957ff277","updated":1776914280151,"created":1776914280151,"links":[{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060847","id":"zettel.20260420060847","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.permanent-note","alias":"permanent-note","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.permanent-note"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060847","id":"zettel.20260420060847","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.software-architecture","alias":"software-architecture","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.software-architecture"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060847","id":"zettel.20260420060847","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.architecture","alias":"architecture","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.architecture"}},{"type":"frontmatterTag","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060847","id":"zettel.20260420060847","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"tags.cost-of-change","alias":"cost-of-change","xvault":false,"to":{"fname":"tags.cost-of-change"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060847","id":"zettel.20260420060847","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":3,"offset":960},"end":{"line":18,"column":52,"offset":1009},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060847","id":"zettel.20260420060847","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.literature.architecture-important-stuff","position":{"start":{"line":19,"column":3,"offset":1065},"end":{"line":19,"column":53,"offset":1115},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.literature.architecture-important-stuff"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060847","id":"zettel.20260420060847","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"zettel.20260420055738","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":3,"offset":1189},"end":{"line":20,"column":28,"offset":1214},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"zettel.20260420055738"}},{"from":{"fname":"zettel","id":"zettel","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":31,"column":3,"offset":1947},"end":{"line":31,"column":28,"offset":1972},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420060847"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420060928","id":"zettel.20260420060928","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":3,"offset":1099},"end":{"line":20,"column":28,"offset":1124},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420060847"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061007","id":"zettel.20260420061007","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":3,"offset":1030},"end":{"line":23,"column":28,"offset":1055},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420060847"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061232","id":"zettel.20260420061232","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":3,"offset":1357},"end":{"line":22,"column":28,"offset":1382},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420060847"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420061356","id":"zettel.20260420061356","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":3,"offset":1351},"end":{"line":23,"column":28,"offset":1376},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420060847"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.20260420062120","id":"zettel.20260420062120","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":22,"column":3,"offset":1346},"end":{"line":22,"column":28,"offset":1371},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420060847"},{"from":{"fname":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","id":"zettel.moc.software-architecture","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":64,"column":3,"offset":4999},"end":{"line":64,"column":28,"offset":5024},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260420060847"}],"anchors":{},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"arsitektur-adalah-penentu-biaya-perubahan-masa-depan\">Arsitektur adalah penentu biaya perubahan masa depan<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#arsitektur-adalah-penentu-biaya-perubahan-masa-depan\"></a></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Di paragraf pembuka, Fowler menggeser fokus dari definisi formal arsitektur ke efek ekonomi dari keputusan desain: jika arsitektur jelek, menambah kemampuan baru akan lebih lambat dan lebih mahal.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Catatan gue:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fowler membuka dengan mengakui bahwa kata \"architecture\" kabur di industri software.</li>\n<li>Dia kemudian menempatkannya sebagai ukuran ekonomi: apakah desain sistem akan membuat perubahan berikutnya murah atau mahal.</li>\n<li>Ini menolak arsitektur sebagai dekorasi teknis atau status simbol; arsitektur adalah ukuran kritikal dari biaya perubahan masa depan.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Implikasi:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Diskusi arsitektur harus dimulai dari pertanyaan \"apakah ini akan membuat perubahan berikutnya lebih sulit?\" bukan \"apakah ini terlihat seperti arsitektur?\"</li>\n<li>Keputusan arsitektur paling berguna ketika ia mengidentifikasi elemen yang mahal jika salah.</li>\n<li>Tim yang mengabaikan arsitektur tidak sedang menghemat waktu; mereka sedang meminjam kecepatan dari masa depan.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Hubungan:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.software-architecture-guide\">Software Architecture Guide — Fowler: arsitektur sebagai keputusan penting dan mahal kalau salah</a> — literatur dari halaman Software Architecture Guide</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.architecture-important-stuff\">Arsitektur adalah apa yang paling penting, bukan hanya struktur tinggi</a> — literatur yang menekankan arsitektur sebagai apa yang paling penting</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420055738\">Software architecture adalah jaringan keputusan trade-off, bukan sekadar diagram</a> — arsitektur sebagai jaringan keputusan trade-off</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">permanent-note (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">software-architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">architecture (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">cost-of-change (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420060928\">Arsitektur bukan kasta; dia harus hidup bersama kode</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420061007\">Halaman Software Architecture Guide adalah peta keputusan, bukan tutorial implementasi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420061232\">Fowler memulai definisi arsitektur dengan kritik terhadap ‘fundamental organization’</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420061356\">Arsitektur bukan sekadar keputusan awal proyek</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260420062120\">Cruft adalah utang kebingungan yang memperlambat perubahan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"ena